LayoutNode.Content: Love the look and feel of this chair! It was easy to assemble. All you have to do is screw in theplastic legs to the bottom and you’re finished. The fabric is in a soft, velvety dark blue. Lookstrue to the item description pic. Lint, pet fur and other fibers will stick to the fabric so you’ll haveto wipe it down or vacuum when needed. It’s comfortable to sit in but the seat cushion is a littlefirm. I’m sure it will soften after some use. It’s not a child-sized chair. The seat itself is about 20inches wide and narrows toward the back. From the floor to the top of the seat cushion it sitsabout 17 inches high. It is lightweight so it’s easy to move around. Not so easy to pick upbecause of the round shape and slick, velvety fabric. Trust me, my husband and I carried it upa flight of stairs. The weight capacity is 200-225 pounds. This chair would look great in anyroom. I have mine in my home office and at such an affordable price you could purchase 2. I'mvery pleased with my purchase. See more

It’s comfortable to sit in but the seat cushion is a little firm. I’m sure it will soften after some use. It’s not a child-sized chair. The seat itself is about 20 inches wide and narrows toward the back. From the floor to the top of the seat cushion it sits about 17 inches high. It is lightweight so it’s easy to move around. Not so easy to pick up because of the round shape and slick, velvety fabric. Trust me, my husband and I carried it up a flight of stairs. The weight capacity is 200-225 pounds.
